":"란","body":"나도 노래방은 패스야.\n……그리고 노래방은 저번에도 갔잖아.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event06-05-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"히~짱은 노래방을 너무 좋아한다니까~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"niyaniya01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event06-05-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"히마리","body":"응! 왠지 상쾌해지니까 좋아!\n그리고~ 노래방에 가면 자기도 모르게\n라이브 같은 거 흉내 내고 싶어지지 않아?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event06-05-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"히마리","body":"「오예~! 오늘도 땡큐~!」 같은 거!\n그리고 기타 치는 척 같은 것도 해보고 말이야~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event06-05-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"……난 안 하는데.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":